              },
              "blocks": {
                "accordion_row_yj78wD": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Mwl Design",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_PcEMT3": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Each MWL dress is designed in our design studio by Carla Jenkins and our expert team of designers, pattern makers and seamstresses.  </p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_PcEMT3"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_nL9mgY": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Made To Order",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_NTz9y7": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Enjoy a personalised one on one appointment with a professional stylist. Once you select your gown, it is made to order and expertly crafted to your exact measurements taken during your appointment.</p><p>Each dress is individually produced, with its creation carefully scheduled to align with your wedding date.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_NTz9y7"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_amkLhB": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How Do We Work?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_WLU8Fi": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>During your appointment, our trained stylists will guide you in selecting the most suitable size for your body, including split sizing where required. Your chosen size, measurements, and stylist notes are carefully recorded and used to craft your dress with precision and care.</p><p>In some cases, brides choose to make minor alterations after their dress is delivered, for this reason we can provide recommendations for trusted and affordable local seamstresses. </p><p>To ensure a smooth and efficient process, we do not offer multiple fittings. If you anticipate changes to your measurements, please let your stylist know during your appointment so they can tailor an approach that best supports you.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_WLU8Fi"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_N9VTyq": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How To Place Your Order?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_hWhQxC": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>If you visited one of our flagship boutiques in Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, the Gold Coast, London, Manchester, or Utrecht, our team of dedicated stylists will be delighted to assist you with placing your order and guide you through the process with care. </p><p>If you discovered your dress at one of our authorised retailers, please contact them directly to complete your purchase.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_hWhQxC"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_gqd7kE": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Payment",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_LzGAFQ": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>For orders placed through our MWL boutiques, we offer a range of flexible payment options to choose from. For further information on our payment plans, please speak with your stylist during your appointment or contact us directly at hello@mwlbride.com. </p><p>For online orders, payment can be made in full or via PayPal Pay in 4 for purchases under $2,000 AU.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_LzGAFQ"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_GtQ36q": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Timing And Delivery",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_e33ymt": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>MWL Boutique Brides - </strong>Purchased through a MWL Boutique </p><p>We recommend MWL Boutique brides receive their dress at least two months before the wedding to allow time for alterations and final styling. Standard and priority order options are available, please connect with your stylist to assist with choosing the right option during your appointment. </p><p>For boutique orders, we’ll email your tracking number when your dress ships from our Gold Coast office. A signature is required on delivery. Please try on your dress as soon as possible, without makeup, lotions, or fake tan.</p><p>If you notice any sizing issues, email <a>hello@mwlbride.com</a> within 24 hours of delivery with photos. We’ll work with you to resolve the issue; unfortunately, we cannot cover costs reported after 24 hours.</p><p><strong>International Brides </strong>- Purchased through a MWL Partner </p><p>International brides should contact their local stockist for timelines, rush options and queries relating to their purchase. </p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_e33ymt"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_rpPWcN": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Shipping",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_h6MCJD": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>We ship worldwide on all veils, accessories, and Ready to Wear dresses.</p><p><strong>Free shipping</strong> is available on orders over $220 AU. Orders under $220 incur the below shipping fees.</p><p><strong>Standard shipping fees:</strong><br/><br/>Australia – $10<br/><br/>International – $20</p><p><strong>Express shipping (Australia only via Australia Post):</strong><br/><br/>Veils & accessories – $15 AUD<br/><br/>Ready to Wear dresses – $30 AUD</p><p>Please select express shipping at checkout if required. While express orders are prioritised, dispatch may take up to 3 business days from our Australian HQ.</p><p>For international orders, duties, taxes, and customs fees are not included and are the responsibility of the buyer. These charges are determined by the destination country’s customs authority and are payable upon delivery. Please check with your local customs office for details before purchasing.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
