                },
                "accordion_row_6PdLAV": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Returns",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_ahaDaY": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>Made To Order dresses: </strong></p><p>As each dress is made to order to specific measurements, we are unable to accept returns, exchanges, or offer full refunds on made to order dresses. </p><p>Returns for accessories (excluding earrings and headbands for hygiene reasons) may be accepted if you contact us within 48 hours of receiving your order. Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the buyer.</p><p><strong>Ready to Wear dresses: </strong><br/><br/>• If your Ready to Wear order was placed in-store with assistance from an MWL Boutique stylist, you are eligible for an exchange or credit note if the item is not suitable.<br/><br/>• If your Ready to Wear order was placed online without stylist assistance, we can offer a refund (excluding shipping).</p><p><strong>Accessories: </strong></p><ul><li></li></ul><p>To initiate a Ready to Wear or accessory return, please contact <a><strong>hello@mwlbride.com</strong></a> within 48 hours of receiving your item. Once approved, items must be returned within 14 days (Australia) or 21 days (international). All items must be in original condition and must not be worn, altered, or washed.</p><p><strong>Sale items:</strong></p><ul><li>Sample sale items are <strong>final sale</strong> and cannot be returned or exchanged. Any faults will be clearly described. </li><li>All sale items are <strong>final sale</strong> and cannot be returned or exchanged</li></ul>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
