                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_YHK3gw": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Unfortunately, we cannot offer a return or refund of a made to order dress due to change of mind, if circumstances change or if your wedding is cancelled. If we haven’t started your dress, you are more than welcome to change your order, but we cannot refund. We cannot refund you if you feel that your dress does not suit you, as this dress was made specifically for you.</p>",
