                  "blocks": {
                    "text_Uz8CKe": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>We can be contacted via email at hello@mwlbride.com or on social media at @mwlbride.</p><p>Please allow 24-48 hours for our team to respond to your enquiry. Please note office staff do not work on the weekends, so all emails and DMs sent on the weekend or after 2pm AEST on Fridays will receive a reply the following 1-2 business days. We are based in Queensland, Australia and follow all Public Holidays for the state.</p><p>If you need to cancel your boutique appointment and it is the weekend, we recommend replying to your confirmation text as our emails aren’t monitored on weekends.</p>",
